{"tid":138391,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］吊鐘發炎 大左幾倍點解決","createTime":"2017-02-28T14:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T13:08:30.000Z","uid":3156,"like":9,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dca9bf8ea28cdcf583c98ac8f4016d5c686aa957","tid":138391,"uid":3156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"前幾日喉嚨唔舒服 食野吞口水都痛痛地 <br />\nFeel到有d野 以為係有痰<br />\n<br />\n到琴日夜晚 思前想後 驚覺喉嚨有野又整唔走既原因<br />\n就係個吊鍾 <br />\n<br />\n我去照一照鏡 發現個吊鐘長左好多 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97FP0Ym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97FP0Ym.jpg&h=7038eb10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左今日 情況惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長左又粗左 <br />\n同埋我有鼻敏感 鼻塞 有時要靠個口呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呼吸同講野都feel到佢瘋狂搖擺<br />\n<br />\n正常人 （我家姐）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CB8Lhh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CB8Lhh.jpg&h=d0edf1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/884RWeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F884RWeH.jpg&h=10f23904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD圖有d噁心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好辛苦用前鏡開閃光燈自拍 <br />\n拍一張拍成幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為個吊鐘太巨型 好難影得曬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解決呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"4a844d4119105c5dadec6b7b46239415a1dadd54","tid":138391,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9814c2d91872532632b2b7afeeca8e1500017ade","tid":138391,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"睇醫生囉 唔通隔住個moon 幫你醫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3a93f4df5048a4ce16d5ea63bb637b28e6df45","tid":138391,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"砍掉重練"},{"pid":"8aaacdde4cd7f47424770df728e813d870c0843a","tid":138391,"uid":57693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"飲水 訓 睇醫生"},{"pid":"226c3cca0a2ef44c8b9c6a98061e9921f5b9ee5a","tid":138391,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"發炎"},{"pid":"06fa4d4a1ee07aa75b3962e4fadf167e4b9c450d","tid":138391,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030edee1ebab850a2ab424bf6a67e09e38d28714","tid":138391,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"292d75626dc9ed9c8834b2077df617e0282650fc","tid":138391,"uid":11104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"啲牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e2a69c64ad4e7b86c82f103cf593828b96924","tid":138391,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>砍掉重練</blockquote><br />\nwtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257542068f708d35ab17384114b573ffc3c3c605","tid":138391,"uid":3156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"我岩岩食完檸檬味屎立消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486dd73972f0f7d926555170db1d926c2ff9130a","tid":138391,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"吊鐘生飛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23c514763265847f86a0a8b790dd763f7775fab","tid":138391,"uid":18566,"like":0